title: etnies X Plan B
description:
etnies and Plan B skateboards have reunited to collaborate on a footwear collection. The two brands have had ties since 1992 and today, Chris Joslin and Ryan Sheckler continue the alliance.
Featuring a strategic tactile defense with high-impact rebound STI Evolution® Foam.
Shop the collection: etnies.com/shop/etnies-x-plan-b
